      <div>
        <p><seg type="diplomatic" subtype="address">Norm’ <persName><roleName>vicecomes</roleName></persName> de Berewic . Omnibus hominibus suis de Crostorfin  <seg type="diplomatic" subtype="salutation">salutem</seg>.</seg><lb/> <seg type="diplomatic" subtype="disposition">Sciatis me concessisse . ⁊ in perpetuam elemosinam dedisse . Sancte cruci de<lb/> Edeneb’ . ⁊ abbati . ⁊ fratribus ibidem deo seruientibus . Capellam meam de Cros<lb/>torfin cum omnibus rectitudinibus capelle eidem pertinentibus.</seg> <seg type="diplomatic" subtype="witnesses">T<ex>estibus</ex> . He[n]rico Comite<lb/> ⁊ Edwardo Cancellario . ⁊ Turoldo archidiacono Lodonie . ⁊ Ricardo Cle<lb/>rico de Edeneb’.</seg> Apud Berewic</p>
